atest run when charging home for third over 1400m here was very good. He is looking for more ground now, and if 1600m is not already too short for him, then he is the one to beat for us. 11. STRAWBERRY IMPACT returned from a spell with a big finish to grab third in a Provincial Championships qualifier at Kembla Grange just over 3 weeks ago. He has found it hard to win another race, but he will be a lot stronger this year, and he can get the job done this time. 7. FIDDLERS GREEN won a similar race here two back, then closed off his run too late again at Randwick-Kensington 3 weeks ago. If the gaps open at the right time, then he can have the last say in a field like this. 10. SPIRIT OF CAMELOT disappointed as a warm favourite last start, but he’s better than that, and he has the winkers on for the first time to help him concentrate in the early part of his racing. Don't drop him and follow your money.\",\"runners\":[2,11,7,10],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Darren Flindell","tipRunnerNumbers":[8,2,11,13]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,11,7,10]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,12,11,10]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[13,11,5,1]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,9,4,3]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[11,2,9,13]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[12,5,8,7]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[11,2,12,1]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trif